Fiorice is a flowering plant that exclusively grows in [[Risia]]n [[manifest zone]]s. It resembles a violet with white, blue-streaked petals. These petals, when dropped into a liquid, rapidly freeze it; one petal can freeze up to a half-gallon (2L) of water.